{"id":232892323,"title":"畢業學分門檻問題","content":"各位學長姐好\n我是進修部大二的學生\n明天要選課了所以算了一下自己缺的通識課學分\n但是看到了一個問題 查了很久還是不太明白\n\n這是我的必修學分：\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/e4efde50-a50c-4b04-afcd-d9d9d843dc19/full.jpeg\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/021ea14d-72b7-4601-a26a-580ce009e357/1280.jpeg\n這個必修課表上加起來是77學分\n通識需要修14學分 基本知能需要12學分\n\n我的問題是我還是不明白 必修分數為何是89分\n我怎麼算都得不出這個數字 \n總不可能是77+12吧  那個77分已經包含了這12分了\n除此之外我真的算不出來\n\n2.所以必修89分加系內選20分 \n我還需要19個自由學分 是這樣的意思嗎\n這數字真的超奇怪的\n\n麻煩各位學長姐幫我解惑了 \n因為明天可以開放大二選課\n想儘快了解 感謝各位","excerpt":"各位學長姐好，我是進修部大二的學生，明天要選課了所以算了一下自己缺的通識課學分，但是看到了一個問題 查了很久還是不太明白，這是我的必修學分：這個必修課表上加起來是77學分，通識需要修14學分 基本知能","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"5120400e-e5e6-4676-a1b8-75a13625ecea","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-14T18:04:12.659Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-14T18:10:38.979Z","commentCount":4,"likeCount":1,"tags":[],"topics":["學分","畢業","門檻","課程","選課"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"淡江大學","forumAlias":"tku","school":"淡江大學","department":"企業管理學系","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/e4efde50-a50c-4b04-afcd-d9d9d843dc19/full.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/021ea14d-72b7-4601-a26a-580ce009e357/1280.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"10a14f91-d2e1-4839-8b7b-df3ced100e2f","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/e4efde50-a50c-4b04-afcd-d9d9d843dc19/320.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/e4efde50-a50c-4b04-afcd-d9d9d843dc19/320.jpeg","thumbnail":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/e4efde50-a50c-4b04-afcd-d9d9d843dc19/320.jpeg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-14T18:04